Description: "Crescendo" firmware; ramping UI for clicky-switch lights
  Uses a smooth ramp instead of discrete modes and mode groups.
  Can run on almost any clicky-switch driver.
  Optional memory.
  Has a bunch of optional blinkies / special modes.
Button-Type: clicky
Memory: offtime, mem decay, short-cycle
MCU: attiny13, attiny25, attiny45, attiny85
Authors: ToyKeeper
Modes: ramp, battcheck, tactical strobe, police strobe, bike flasher, SOS, heart beacon, sunset, config
Extras: ramping UI, LVP, thermal regulation, dual PWM
License: GPLv3
